    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税措施胜过对伊朗的制裁，油价料将周度下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对特朗普总统对中国征收关税将削弱需求的担忧超过了美国新政府对伊朗实施第一轮制裁的影响，油价连续第三周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 23:33:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布前，中国推动亚洲股市走高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管日本面临抛售压力，但中国科技股的上涨帮助提振了周五亚洲股市，因为交易员正在等待美国就业数据，这些数据将有助于阐明未来的利率走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:34:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度承诺在莫迪与特朗普会晤前进一步削减关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/india-may-cut-more-import-taxes-as-manufacturing-picks-up-speed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部一位高级官员在印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪访美前表示，随着国内制造业的改善，印度将继续降低关税并逐步取消对进口商品的额外征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/india-may-cut-more-import-taxes-as-manufacturing-picks-up-speed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Seven & i 财团有望获得美国银行和花旗银行的融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/seven-i-consortium-said-to-tap-bofa-citi-for-buyout-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，提议将 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 私有化的财团已获得花旗集团和美国银行的融资，从而让参与这项可能破纪录的管理层收购竞标的财团变得更加强大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/seven-i-consortium-said-to-tap-bofa-citi-for-buyout-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
